WEBVTT

00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:02.676
Maksima "Spoznaj sebe"

00:00:02.700 --> 00:00:04.700
postoji još od stare Grčke.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:07.572
Neki je pripisuju Platonu,

00:00:07.596 --> 00:00:09.215
neki Pitagori,

00:00:09.239 --> 00:00:12.422
ali i nije toliko bitno
koji mudrac ju je prvi koristio,

00:00:12.446 --> 00:00:15.446
već to da se zadržala do današnjih dana.

00:00:16.800 --> 00:00:18.261
Spoznaj sebe.

00:00:18.285 --> 00:00:20.134
Precizno pogađa suštinu,

00:00:20.158 --> 00:00:22.159
gotovo do tačke besmisla,

00:00:22.183 --> 00:00:25.183
ali zvuči poznato i istinito, zar ne?

00:00:25.900 --> 00:00:27.473
Spoznaj sebe.

00:00:28.800 --> 00:00:30.566
Ja ovu bezvremenu sentencu shvatam